{
  "stem": "6130.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Because it was very important, the job, what they were doing, to speak several languages.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And they-- they pretend that they are Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they pretend they are this or that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They-- they did fantastic work for the United States government-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] --risking their lives many times.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Anyhow, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I said, I have to go back, my husband, my brothers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So they took me to Prague, and they put me on a train, which was horrible, because I could feel antisemitism in the-- on the train.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I went to Budapest first.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Because the train stopped there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I had-- I looked up some relatives.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I found out that everybody died in my home, in my family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I was a little later going back than some others, because of [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Yutka ?] and Ike.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And they always told me they would take me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Don't trust, they will take me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And that's why I got there a little later, in October.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Then I went to my hometown.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And close to the-- across the street from the railway station, there's the most beautiful legitimate theater building.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And across from that, there is a park around the theater.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And across from the theater there is a fence, a wooden fence.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And the first thing I see is it said, death on the Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "When I got back to Hungary, to my hometown, that was the first thing I have seen, death on the Jews.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] Well, I was scared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So of course, I told you before, they didn't let me into my parents' house, or my house.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I found a friend who had an apartment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To apartments, it was easier to get back than to a home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I stayed with her.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
